---
title: Honey and Soy-Smothered Pork with Roasted Veggies and Rice
description: Pork tenderloin is one of our favorite cuts because it's lean, juicy, and (as its name suggests), impeccably tender. Its flavor is on the mild side, though, which means that you've gotta dress it up with flavorful seasonings. Here, we're adding a glaze that's equal parts savory, sweet, and piquant from the mix of soy sauce, honey, and mustard, then rounding it out with roasted veggies.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soy-glazed-pork-with-blistered-asian-veg-d8e088e7.jpg
